						               													<description>A 2-4 player party game based around taking crowdfunding campaigns, represented by the blue &amp;quot;Pitch&amp;quot; cards, and creating a chain of events resulting in the campaign's failure by taking turns placing &amp;quot;Ploy&amp;quot; cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the beginning of a round, a Pitch card is drawn to represent that round's campaign. Each player will then take turns playing Ploys that tie in not only with the initial Pitch, but every Ploy currently in play. This cycle will continue as long as players have cards they can contribute.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Unlike games like Cards Against Humanity and Joking Hazard, the winner of a round is determined by the total amount of cards they played. The winner will then take the Pitch card for their &amp;quot;Hall of Shame&amp;quot;. The first player to get 5 Pitches in their Hall of Shame wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each card in the game is based around campaigns that were pitched on crowdfunding sites like Kickstarter and Indiegogo.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
